edu.umass.cs.gigapaxos.paxospackets

Class PaxosPacket

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.nio.JSONPacket
      • edu.umass.cs.gigapaxos.paxospackets.PaxosPacket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Summarizable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AcceptReplyPacket, BatchedAccept, BatchedCommit, BatchedPaxosPacket, FailureDetectionPacket, FindReplicaGroupPacket, PreparePacket, PrepareReplyPacket, RequestPacket, StatePacket, SyncDecisionsPacket

    public abstract class PaxosPacket
extends JSONPacket
implements Summarizable
    Author:
    arun The parent class for all paxos packet types. Every paxos packet has a minimum of three fields: packet type, paxos group ID, version.
